value.0: With a roar of ice and snow, the cave entrance has sealed behind you. You can't get out!

This magical device bears a unique hallmark that looks like an open book. Created by a powerful mage, this apparently indestructible device appears to be imbued with magic that will lure the great white dragon back to her cave. It's not entirely clear what it does exactly, but Frostspear clearly doesn't like it.

// Activated by using Greater Mythal on it. Once enough have been used, it will activate the boss fight. Only one mythal may be used per character. Be warned: This is dangerous!
